# Global Design System

## Color System (Strict)

- Background: `#0B0E11` (`var(--color-bg)`) or existing dark surfaces.
- Brand yellow `#F0B90B` (`var(--color-brand)`) **ONLY** for:
  - Primary CTA buttons (申购, 立即租赁, 确认, Connect, Submit)
  - Selected tab **underlines** (not tab text/icons unless underline)
- Earning green `#0ECB81` (`var(--color-earn)`) **ONLY** for:
  - Earning rate data (APY, ROI %, positive yield numbers)
  - **Never** use for buttons or badges
- Loss red `#F6465D` (`var(--color-loss)`) **ONLY** for:
  - Negative PnL, losses, sell-side destructive actions
- Greys for all other text, borders, inactive states.

## Typography

- Use `var(--font-number)` + `font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums` for **all numbers** (balances, rates, prices, APY).
- Apply class `.num` or semantic classes: `.apy-value`, `.data-value`, `.total-amount`.

## Component Radii

| Element | Radius | Token |
|---------|--------|-------|
| Buttons | 8px | `var(--radius-button)` |
| Inputs | 12px | `var(--radius-input)` |
| Cards | 16px | `var(--radius-card)` |

## CSS Usage

Prefer design tokens from `src/styles/design-tokens.css` over hardcoded hex values.

```css
.btn-cta {
  background: var(--color-brand);
  color: #000;
  border-radius: var(--radius-button);
}
.text-earn { color: var(--color-earn); }
.text-loss { color: var(--color-loss); }
```
